.TH HYPER-COMPLETIONS 1 "January 2026" "hyper 0.1.0" "CI/CD Hyper-A Manual"
.SH NAME
hyper-completions \- generate shell completion scripts
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hyper completions
.I SHELL
[\fB\-\-output\fR \fIDIR\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hyper completions
generates shell completion scripts for various shells. These scripts enable
tab-completion of commands, options, and arguments.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
.I SHELL
Target shell: \fBbash\fR, \fBzsh\fR, \fBfish\fR, \fBelvish\fR, or \fBpowershell\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-output =\fIDIR\fR
Output directory for completion file. If not specified, outputs to stdout.
.SH INSTALLATION
.SS Bash
Add to \fB~/.bashrc\fR:
.PP
.RS
.nf
eval "$(hyper completions bash)"
.fi
.RE
.PP
Or pre-generate:
.PP
.RS
.nf
hyper completions bash > ~/.local/share/bash-completion/completions/hyper
.fi
.RE
.SS Zsh
Add to \fB~/.zshrc\fR:
.PP
.RS
.nf
mkdir -p ~/.zsh/completions
hyper completions zsh > ~/.zsh/completions/_hyper
fpath=(~/.zsh/completions $fpath)
autoload -Uz compinit && compinit
.fi
.RE
.SS Fish
Run once:
.PP
.RS
.nf
hyper completions fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/hyper.fish
.fi
.RE
.SS Elvish
Add to \fB~/.elvish/rc.elv\fR:
.PP
.RS
.nf
eval (hyper completions elvish | slurp)
.fi
.RE
.SS PowerShell
Add to \fB$PROFILE\fR:
.PP
.RS
.nf
Invoke-Expression (& hyper completions powershell | Out-String)
.fi
.RE
.SH EXIT CODES
.TP
.B 0
Completion script generated successfully.
.TP
.B 1
Invalid shell or generation error.
.SH EXAMPLES
Output bash completions to stdout:
.PP
.RS
.nf
hyper completions bash
.fi
.RE
.PP
Generate zsh completions to file:
.PP
.RS
.nf
hyper completions zsh -o ~/.zsh/completions/
.fi
.RE
.PP
Show installation instructions:
.PP
.RS
.nf
hyper completions --help
.fi
.RE
